You can use these queryable attributes to filter this collection resource using the q query parameter:
  • accountType; string; The type of transaction the distribution represents, such as expense, revenue, and so forth.
  • accountTypeCode; string; The code that identifies the type of transaction the distribution represents, such as expense, revenue, and so forth.
  • accountedCurrencyCode; string; The currency code of accounting currency of the source joint venture transaction.
  • accountingDate; string; The date used to determine the accounting period for the transaction.
  • accountingHeaderId; integer; The unique identifier of the joint venture accounting header.
  • agreement; string; The name of the agreement of the carried interest distribution.
  • agreementDescription; string; The description of the agreement of the carried interest distribution.
  • applicationId; integer; The unique identifier of the functional area for subledger accounting.
  • assignmentRule; string; The name of the ownership definition assignment rule used to assign the ownership definition or direct billed stakeholder.
  • businessUnit; string; The name of the business unit associated with the joint venture.
  • carriedInterestOwnershipDefinition; string; The name of the ownership definition used to process the distribution.
  • changeReason; string; The reason the carried interest distribution was changed.
  • changeReasonDetails; string; Additional text to describe the reason the carried interest distribution was changed.
  • consentingPercentage; number; The percentage of the nonconsenting stakeholder's share that's assumed by the consenting stakeholder.
  • consentingStakeholder; string; The name of the consenting stakeholder on the carried interest distribution.
  • createdBy; string; The user who created the joint venture distribution.
  • creationDate; string; The date and time when the joint venture distribution was created.
  • distributedAccount; string; The combination of the values of the account segments assigned to the transaction.
  • distributedAccountedCredit; number; The distributed credit amount for the stakeholder in accounting currency.
  • distributedAccountedDebit; number; The distributed debit amount for the stakeholder in accounting currency.
  • distributedEnteredCredit; number; The distributed credit amount for the stakeholder in the entered currency.
  • distributedEnteredDebit; number; The distributed debit amount for the stakeholder in the entered currency.
  • distributionId; integer; The unique identifier of a carried interest distribution.
  • distributionLineNumber; integer; The line number used when a carried interest distribution record is reversed, reassigned, or redistributed.
  • distributionLineType; string; The type of carried interest distribution line, such as original, canceled, reversed, and so forth.
  • endDate; string; The end date of the effective date range of the ownership definition.
  • enteredCurrencyCode; string; The currency code entered on the original transaction.
  • expenditureType; string; The name identifying the expenditure classification.
  • expenditureTypeDescription; string; The description of the expenditure type.
  • headerId; integer; The unique identifier of the journal.
  • jointVenture; string; The name of the joint venture associated with the carried interest distribution.
  • jointVentureDescription; string; The description of the joint venture associated with the carried interest distribution.
  • lastUpdateDate; string; The date and time when the joint venture distribution was last updated.
  • lastUpdatedBy; string; The user who last updated the joint venture distribution.
  • ledger; string; The name of the ledger.
  • lineNumber; integer; The number of the journal line.
  • nonConsentingDistributedAccountedCredit; number; The distributed credit amount for the nonconsenting stakeholder in the accounting currency.
  • nonConsentingDistributedAccountedDebit; number; The distributed debit amount for the nonconsenting stakeholder in the accounting currency.
  • nonConsentingDistributedEnteredCredit; number; The distributed credit amount for the nonconsenting stakeholder in the entered currency.
  • nonConsentingDistributedEnteredDebit; number; The distributed debit amount for the nonconsenting stakeholder in the entered currency.
  • nonConsentingPercentage; number; The nonconsenting stakeholder's ownership percentage from the source ownership definition.
  • nonConsentingStakeholder; string; The name of the nonconsenting stakeholder on the carried interest distribution.
  • originalConsentingStakeholder; string; The joint venture stakeholder that was the original consenting stakeholder assuming the share for the nonconsenting stakeholder on the distribution line.
  • originalDistributionId; integer; The unique identifier of the original carried interest distribution line.
  • originalSourceApplication; string; The name of the application the transaction originated from, for example Payables or Cost Management.
  • originalTransactionId; string; The unique identifier of the original transaction.
  • period; string; The accounting period name in a calendar.
  • projectName; string; The name of the project.
  • projectNumber; string; The unique identifier of the project.
  • sourceOwnershipDefinition; string; The original ownership definition assigned to the joint venture transaction that the distribution was created from.
  • sourceOwnershipEndDate; string; The end date of the effective date range of the ownership definition that's the source of the carried interest ownership definition.
  • sourceOwnershipStartDate; string; The start date of the effective date range of the ownership definition that's the source of the carried interest ownership definition.
  • startDate; string; The start date of the effective date range of the ownership definition.
  • status; string; The status of the carried interest distribution.
  • taskName; string; The name of the project task representing a subdivision of work.
  • taskNumber; string; The unique number of the project task.
  • transactionAccountedCredit; number; The transaction credit amount in accounting currency.
  • transactionAccountedDebit; number; The transaction debit amount in accounting currency.
  • transactionDate; string; The transaction date of the carried interest distribution.
  • transactionDescription; string; The description of the general ledger journal entry line.
  • transactionEnteredCredit; number; The transaction credit amount in the entered currency.
  • transactionEnteredDebit; number; The transaction debit amount in the entered currency.
  • transactionId; integer; The unique identifier for the joint venture transaction that the distribution was created from.

    • searchAllText; string; A search value to identify carried interest distributions that contain the specified text in any of the string attributes.
    • sourceOwnershipDefinition; string; The original ownership definition assigned to the joint venture transaction that the distribution was created from.
    • startDate; string; The start date of the effective date range of the ownership definition.
    • status; string; The status; string; of the carried interest distribution.
    • taskName; string; The name of the project task representing a subdivision of work.
    • taskNumber; string; The unique number of the project task.
    • transactionDate; string; The transaction date of the carried interest distribution.
    • transactionDescription; string; The description of the general ledger; string; journal entry line.

item.description: The carried interest subledger distribution resource is used to view or update carried interest subledger distributions.
